        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>mango chutney</strong>, <strong>sriracha</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>mayo</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>mango-sriracha dip</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
