    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, drizzle a little <strong>olive oil </strong>over the<strong> salad</strong> and sprinkle over the<strong> remaining nigella seeds</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>free range</strong> <strong>chicken curry pasty</strong> with the <strong>chips</strong>,<strong> salad</strong> and <strong>mango-sriracha dip </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
